pageTitle: Wednesday's Preseason Friendly vs. Columbus to be Live Streamed | Chicago Fire
TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {24850=Going forward, the likelihood is that the team’s games during phase two of preseason out in California will not have a live video stream but Chicago-Fire.com will at least carry audio of the first team matches vs. Chivas USA (February 5) and San Jose Earthquakes (February 9)., 24135=This means that five of seven 2013 Chicago Fire preseason matches will be carried with live video and all seven will have live coverage here on Chicago-Fire.com., 26088=Coming on the heels of our debut 2013 webcast (and having worked out a few cobwebs in the process), we’re happy to announce that Wednesday’s preseason friendly vs. the Columbus Crew will be live streamed once again on Chicago-Fire.com beginning at 10:30am CT.}
